## Entity Relationship Summary

```
df_master (1 question)
    ├──< df_question_nodes    (1–3 nodes per question)
    ├──< df_question_errors   (1–3 errors per question)
    ├──< df_question_concepts (2–4 concepts per question)
    └──< student_responses    (1 row per student per question attempted)

layer_1_PN:  topic ──→ topic  (75 directed edges)

prerequisite_final.json:  skill ──→ [topics]  (42 skills, each affecting 3–6 topics)
```

